## List:
List are represent data in your page

^^ Mostly two type of list 
order list and unorder list.

^^Unorder list:
syntex:
<ul>
<li>your data,</li>
</ul>

example:
<ul>
<li>Gym</li>
<li>JavaScript</li>
<li>IELTS</li>
</ul>

output:
Gym
JavaScript
IELTS

^^imp: it will give you list without number just bullet point.
you can change bulletpoint by css

^^ Order list:
syntex:
<ol>
<li> your data<li>
</ol>

example:
<ol>
  <li>Wake up</li>
  <li>Workout</li>
  <li>Study JavaScript</li>
</ol>

output:
1.Wake up
2.Workout
3.Study JavaScript

^^ it will give your number with it

